'PCFDF
'PCFT 16
'PCFO 1, 1, 5, 1, 1
'PCFL IID 20 4
'PCFL ICLAS 20 4
'PCFL ICDES 20 60
'PCFL ICGL 20 40
'PCFL ICCOGA 20 40
